source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_00<tab>Mogoot is watching the nearby golems with a keen eye.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_00<tab>オール・ターンのモグートは、辺りの様子を伺っているようだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_01<tab>Mogoot's assignment is to take down limestone golems. He uses this opportunity to express doubt regarding your qualifications to be the Mog Squad's commander. Slay three golems and bring Mogoot their cores to show him your mettle.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_01<tab>モグートは<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>の討伐を目標としているようだ。オール・ターンの「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>」から「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AF101 /var>」を3個入手しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_02<tab>The golems crumble into pebbles before you. Bring their cores back to Mogoot.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>を入手した。オール・ターンの「モグート」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_03<tab>Mogoot is astounded by your fighting skills, and doubts that he will ever be able reach such dizzying heights. His mission complete, he returns to think on what he learned.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_SEQ_03<tab>モグートに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8AF101 /var>を渡した。冒険者の実力はわかったが、同じように戦うのは無理と言って帰ってしまった。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_TODO_00<tab>Slay limestone golems for their cores.
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_000<tab>My assigned training targets are just over there. The golems cannot escape the watchful eye of Mogoot, sniper extraordinaire!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_000<tab>今、目標の敵を……観察しているくぽ……。
あの<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>はモグの眼から逃れられないくぽ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_001<tab>I did have something to ask of you, however. Although I trust Mogzun's judgment, I want to see our commander's strength for myself, kupo. Attest to your strength by bringing me three cores from the limestone golems hulking around the area.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_001<tab>ところで……教官の実力が気になるくぽ。
モグの教官にふさわしいかどうか……見せてほしいくぽ……。
……「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>の心核」を3個……持ってくるくぽ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_010<tab>I would see your battle prowess for myself. Take down the golems that're lumbering about the area.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_010<tab>ところで……教官の実力が気になるくぽ。
モグの教官にふさわしいかどうか……見せてほしいくぽ……。
……「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>の心核」を3個……持ってくるくぽ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_020<tab>The golems crumbled as dirt before your wrath! Did you bring their cores, kupo?
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_020<tab>ところで……教官の実力が気になるくぽ。
モグの教官にふさわしいかどうか……見せてほしいくぽ……。
……「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20E2501 /var>の心核」を3個……持ってくるくぽ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_021<tab>Yes, these will do splendidly! After seeing you fight, I believe the Mog Squad could ask for no more qualified a commander! In fact, I doubt I'll ever be able to defend my home so skillfully... Well, one must know their weaknesses to improve on them! Drill over, kupo!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ518_01853_MOGOOT_000_021<tab>さすが……教官くぽ、認めるくぽ。
見事な戦い……同じように戦うのは、モグには無理くぽ……。
とても勉強になった……訓練終了くぽ！
